e. Materially speaking, Black is +1. However, those 4 pawns are currently useless and Black lost one of the few active pieces he had. How could this be ok for him?! White's king is safeguarded by the surrounding pieces so there's not much you should worry about. Play actively on the kingside and you will be fine.} *

