ack is not convinced by those threats.} 18. Qh8+ Kf7 19. g6+ Kxg6 20. Qh5+ Kf6 21. Qf5+ Ke7 22. Rxe5+ Kd6 23. Rxd5+ Ke7 24. Rh3 {Black will be checkmated in the middle of the board.} *

